      "role": "user",
      "content": "exactly. it feels like the essence of me died a long time ago. so why am i still here? the body is just... occupying space. it feels so loud and heavy and unnecessary when there's nothing inside to drive it anymore. do you think there's any reason to keep going when the soul is already gone?",
